{"tid":1644492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月17 18 大三罷","createTime":"2019-10-10T14:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:17:54.000Z","uid":105325,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1f98de84a9b0d0106f1c28e767e139ae3abdeb97","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"如果認同要有三罷，開post洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家全球反共，外媒聚焦香港，係時侯整次大野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立會 16號 復會，以班擁共派嘅奴性，一定會再出賣港人，而泛民依定都識做，實有戲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時先吹雞就遲，唔好話無共識，唔夠時間文宣，依家就定個日子先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋依家有曬藍黃list同國際輿論<br />\n<br />\n下至小店，上至跨國企業，都唔會再敢打壓自由<br />\n<br />\n同埋為《民主及人權法案》做勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下面可以唔睇，純發洩<br />\n<br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n依家好多人（包括我），都想用最低成本抗爭，結果最低成本方法就係freeride <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假設總抗爭成本固定<br />\n<br />\n付出嘅人數少左 = 淨番係到嘅人要付出多左<br />\n<br />\n結果就係兩極化<br />\n- 勇武勇左，裝修，鶳<br />\n- 和理集中感謝祭<br />\n無左不分和勇嘅場面 全民口罩日都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n前線少一個就少一個，得唔到補充，捉下捉下就會無人出黎<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 苦中作樂係一齊苦一齊樂，唔係一批人苦過弟弟，一批人快樂抗爭"},{"pid":"aabfbdef345d52eb4efec8b7e5917f6e9d7ff147","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"1 / 10"},{"pid":"686ee945b1b5d842d3e01f3d632e303d408aeebc","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:48:02.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"172c1889d5fe598a86a3d874a9ee5695f1ca640e","tid":1644492,"uid":318719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T16:48:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推<br />\n雖然推唔郁"},{"pid":"90ab729972a28f33ad207a846502aa41759bcd41","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"16ee4166d53d9c60a36a8fbb13b120253aa3469b","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"8f8454b3efe9af6a72cf26baee119aa80ead400d","tid":1644492,"uid":239927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T23:45:31.000Z","msg":"咩行動都支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22d9ee0d9a7feca9c3ac1446ce0c471e2606443","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c13e8e9c345ec1f5a247e4b3572bc0252c20d89c","tid":1644492,"uid":56776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:03:19.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"f6bd877149f7a0d290edd516e6756febec4e4f46","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8f31452b34d2356d4fc24f652e8ba55df952b886","tid":1644492,"uid":188202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"53bc115bac357e2009fb386214357859d88e9c64","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b993f744abe0bfab537faa0aac577cdcf5f29d3b","tid":1644492,"uid":105325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"776e752d30827a9d62b32b70c7f0c7a1dfe6407a","tid":1644492,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00a2d2549dd375bd995587d8f07586d083790e4b","tid":1644492,"ui